           </div>
           <div class="p-6 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 space-y-5">

              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                 <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-3">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">1. 观察与建仓 (R0-R2)</h4>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                        <li><strong>R0 观察</strong>: 收盘价高于平行趋势线上轨。</li>
                        <li><strong>R1 建仓</strong>: 突破趋势线+连续2天放量 (>1.5x)。次日回踩确认买入。</li>
                        <li><strong>R2 加仓</strong>: 窗口期10天内，回调至黄金分割位+触碰通道支撑+缩量。</li>
                    </ul>
